[inspiration de surprise]

10
00:01:11,208 --> 00:01:12,875
[murmure] Je crois que c'est lui.

11
00:01:12,958 --> 00:01:13,958
[inspiration]

12
00:01:15,875 --> 00:01:16,833
[grincement]

13
00:01:20,416 --> 00:01:23,166
[musique espiègle]

14
