29
00:02:26,583 --> 00:02:28,000
[inspiration paniquée]

30
00:02:28,791 --> 00:02:30,791
[musique intense]

31
00:02:34,833 --> 00:02:36,625
- [grognement]
- [panique]

32
00:02:43,291 --> 00:02:44,125
[garçon] Ah.

33
00:02:44,208 --> 00:02:45,083
[cri]

34
00:02:45,166 --> 00:02:46,833
[elle hurle]

35
00:02:51,083 --> 00:02:51,916
