sage.

40
00:03:08,166 --> 00:03:09,416
[Leah pleure]

41
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,291
[haut-le-cœur]

42
00:03:22,416 --> 00:03:23,708
[renifle]

43
00:03:26,250 --> 00:03:28,166
William...

44
00:03:29,250 --> 00:03:31,250
- [William gémit]
- [renifle]

45
00:03:34,083 --> 00:03:36,083
[musique intense]

46
00:03:38,250 --> 00:03:40,250
... sage.

47
00:03:41,250 --> 00:03:42,916
